element.name: Dublin's Railway Termini: Bonus Cache by Bootle, Unknown Cache (3/1)
element.long-description:
NOTE: The above coordinates will not bring you to this cache!
This cache is a bonus cache for the "Dublin's Railway Termini" cache series. In order to get the correct coordinates for this cache you must find the 6 caches in this series. Using the numbers that were printed in these caches, the coordinates for this cache can be worked out as
N53 (AxG).({I+C}x{K+H}) W6 (B+J).({F+L}x{DxE}).
These coordinates will bring you to an area that is linked with the railways. All the housing in the immediate area and the surrounding streets were built to serve the workers on the nearby railway. The name of the surrounding streets should tell you which railway company constructed the dwellings!

ul.li:
2010-02-14T20:00:00Z : Found it by Toffee Man
Started of the day with this bonus cache. We had the co-ords for a while & found it easily enough. TFTC Toffee man. #181

2010-02-14T20:00:00Z : Found it by Blue Jay 59
Had the info collected for this for a while. Just got around to picking up the bonus today. Nice houses & square. Enjoyed the series. TFTC & for the series. Blue Jay 59 #182

2010-02-07T20:00:00Z : Found it by Zoe andDaddy
A really nice series, well worth it.
Found while out for a full day caching with Mr Frezeluberz. 40/51
Nice quick cache and dash.
Thanks

2010-02-07T20:00:00Z : Found it by Lahtac
Nice to finish this series off sucesfully. Lovely location. TFTC

2010-02-07T20:00:00Z : Found it by Frezeluberz
Found while out for the day with Zoe andDaddy. So, here we are with all the clues in hand. It's been a long day - time for some mental arithmetic. K + H != K * H That'll get you every time!! Oops [:I] [:I] With no hint and it now being dark we're happy to have had assistance from previous logs. Found quickly after that. No 40 of 50 for the day. TFTC and TFT Series - very satisfying.
